635
00:41:29,960 --> 00:41:31,880
Stačilo by mu iba odobrať jeho titul.

636
00:41:31,960 --> 00:41:34,190
Kim Jong Jikova zrada je jasná,
ako denné svetlo!

637
00:41:34,460 --> 00:41:36,830
Snažíte sa zastávať zradcu?

638
00:41:37,060 --> 00:41:38,410
Vaše Veličenstvo!

639
00:41:38,490 --> 00:41:39,680
Stráže!

640
00:41:39,760 --> 00:41:42,360
